<headline>Special Weather Statement issued March 31 at 2:03PM MDT  by NWS Riverton</headline>
<description>...Snow Showers Tonight...
This is a special weather statement from the National Weather
Service Office in Riverton.
* WHAT...Snow showers. Accumulations of around 1 inch in the lower
elevations; 3 to 5 inches on Casper Mountain.
* WHERE...Natrona County.
* WHEN...Tonight into Friday morning.
* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Motorists should be prepared for rapidly
changing visibility. Roads may become slick, especially after
midnight.</description>
